Class TablePageCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.jerrydog.RequestCallback

            • ca.uqac.lif.labpal.server.TemplatePageCallback
              • ca.uqac.lif.labpal.server.TablePageCallback

  • public class TablePageCallback
extends TemplatePageCallback
    Callback producing a file from one of the lab's tables, in various formats.

    The HTTP request accepts the following parameters:

    • id=x: mandatory; the ID of the table to display
    • format=x: the requested image format. Currenly supports tex, csv and html.
    Author:
    Sylvain Hallé
